Addressing Your Research Needs

Otis Chadley
Subjects:African American Studies, Anthropology, Family Science, Psychology, Sociology

Welcome!

This online course tutorial will assist students of ANTH 472/672: Medical Anthropology.  It will help you in locating print and electronic resources on topics related to Medical Anthropology, including ethnographic studies.  Also, the tutorial includes tips on how to prepare an annotated bibliography.  Always consult with your course instructor for specific requirements regarding your assignments.
